nodes.text: This unidentified Weequay pirate was the captain of a band of Weequay pirates aboard a Corona-class armed frigate.

In 0 ABY, this Weequay pirate made a deal with the Galactic Empire to attack the Rebel escort frigate Redemption, so that Commander Silam Dunerz could earn the trust of Princess Leia Organa. However, the Weequay pirate exceeded the terms of his agreement when he boarded the Rebel ship with his men.
